To those who thinks Rangers aren't the best taunters amongst melee - which means getting and keeping agro - then they should play a Ranger.<br>
<br>
There is a misconception about Rangers : Rangers have the fastest weapons, the least hps with monks and are limited in there armor choice for 60lvls and though u see rangers lvl60 . . . because we can tank, we can heal, we can travel easily and so on.<br>
<br>
About taunts, yes i can steal and keep agro from a lot of people but i wont do it can it is not my purpose except when MA in group and i can regain agro from any Very High Taunt Spell from Necro, Chanter or shamy and i saved many times their life ; About Tanking, Rangers with appropriate stuff can tank as good as any other class though we have a bit less hps and aren't allowed to use plate armor.<br>
Having a ranger as MA is the best way for a Caster to feel safe.<br>
<br>
To come back to the original question about Best Overall Meleer, i will just say Hybrids are the best : Rangers, Paladins and Sks each in there different way. Those classes are Multipurpose meleers and i will just point a thing that is stupid : those 3 classes are those the least known by others, and the more discredited : funny thing.<br>
<br>
Just learn about other classes and u will learn a lot about your safety.<br>
